---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
const base = import.meta.env.BASE_URL;
---

<Layout title="About Me - Triathlon Coaching">
  <h1>About Your Coach</h1>
  
  <section>
    <h2>Experience & Credentials</h2>
    <p>
      As a dedicated triathlon coach with years of experience in endurance sports, I'm
      passionate about helping athletes of all levels achieve their triathlon goals.
    </p>
    <p>
      My coaching philosophy is built on the principles of structured training,
      progressive overload, and personalized attention. I believe that every athlete
      is unique and deserves a training plan that fits their individual needs,
      lifestyle, and aspirations.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>My Approach</h2>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Individualized Training:</strong> Every plan is customized to your specific needs and goals</li>
      <li><strong>Data-Driven:</strong> Using the latest sports science and performance metrics</li>
      <li><strong>Holistic Development:</strong> Focus on all three disciplines plus nutrition and recovery</li>
      <li><strong>Continuous Support:</strong> Regular check-ins and plan adjustments as needed</li>
    </ul>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>Why Work With Me?</h2>
    <p>
      I understand the challenges of balancing training with work, family, and other
      commitments. My coaching approach is flexible and sustainable, designed to help
      you improve while maintaining a healthy life balance.
    </p>
    <p>
      Whether you're targeting a sprint triathlon or an Ironman, I'll be with you
      every step of the way, providing expert guidance, motivation, and support.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section>
    <p>
      <a href={`${base}/contact`} class="cta-button">Start Your Journey</a>
    </p>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  h1 {
    color: var(--accent);
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  section {
    margin: 3rem 0;
  }

  ul {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
  }

  ul li {
    padding: 0.5rem 0;
    padding-left: 1.5rem;
    position: relative;
  }

  ul li::before {
    content: "â†’";
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    color: var(--accent);
    font-weight: bold;
  }

  .cta-button {
    display: inline-block;
    background: var(--accent);
    color: var(--white);
    padding: 1rem 2rem;
    text-decoration: none;
    border-radius: 4px;
    font-weight: 600;
    transition: background 0.2s;
  }

  .cta-button:hover {
    background: var(--accent-dark);
  }
</style>
